TRANG 1: TRANG CHU (/)
Muc tieu:
Gioi thieu Linh Hoa Tam nhu mot khong gian thuat so hoc hien dai, chua lanh va de ung dung; dan nguoi dung den dich vu va lien he.

Section 1 - Hero
- Eyebrow: Thuat So Hoc hien dai
- Headline: Hieu ro ban than de song thuan nhip, sang huong va ben vung hon.
- Mo ta: nhan manh trai nghiem tinh te, chua lanh, ket noi nang luong ca nhan, moi quan he va hanh trinh su nghiep.
- CTA 1: Kham pha ngay -> /#dich-vu
- CTA 2: Xem y nghia con so cua ban -> /#lien-he
- 3 diem nhan gia tri:
  + Tu duy dinh huong
  + Chua lanh noi tam
  + Chuyen sau so hoc
- Khoi visual ben phai gioi thieu Linh Hoa Tam va 3 tu khoa:
  + Ngay sinh
  + So chu dao
  + Dinh huong

Section 2 - Gioi thieu
ID neo: gioi-thieu
- Tieu de lon: Linh Hoa Tam la khong gian de ban lang nghe ban than qua chieu sau cua thuat so hoc.
- Mo ta: tiep can hien dai, tinh te, chua lanh; chuyen hoa so chu dao, ngay sinh va chi so ca nhan thanh goc nhin ro rang va de ap dung.
- Cot trai nhan manh 2 gia tri:
  + Ket noi noi tam
  + Dinh huong thuc te
- 3 the gia tri bo sung:
  + Thau hieu
  + Khai mo
  + Ben vung

Section 3 - Dich vu
ID neo: dich-vu
- Tieu de lon: Nhung trai nghiem duoc thiet ke de ban hieu ro hon ve con so, cam xuc va huong di cua minh.
- Mo ta: can bang giua chieu sau chuyen mon va cam giac de tiep can.
- 4 nhom dich vu hien co:
  1. Xem than so hoc ca nhan
  2. Phan tich ngay sinh
  3. Y nghia cac con so
  4. Tu van dinh huong ban than

Section 4 - Bai viet noi bat
- Tieu de lon: Nhung bai viet moi ve thuat so hoc, dinh huong ban than va cac ket noi chua lanh.
- Mo ta: kho noi dung nhe nhang, hien dai, co the ung dung trong doi song.
- Hien thi 3 bai viet noi bat.
- CTA: Xem tat ca bai viet -> /tin-tuc

Section 5 - Cam nhan khach hang
- Tieu de lon: Nhung chia se chan that tu nguoi da dong hanh cung Linh Hoa Tam.
- Mo ta: nhan manh cam giac duoc lang nghe, soi sang va dong hanh.
- Dang hien thi 3 testimonial mau:
  + Ngoc Han - Nguoi di lam
  + Mai An - Chu kinh doanh nho
  + Tu Linh - Nguoi dang tim dinh huong

Section 6 - Lien he
ID neo: lien-he
- Tieu de lon: Bat dau hanh trinh kham pha con so cua ban bang mot cuoc tro chuyen diu dang va chuyen sau.
- Mo ta: phu hop cho nguoi muon hieu ro hon ve ban than, cong viec va moi quan he.
- Khoi noi dung bo tro:
  + Phan tich nhe nhang, ro rang va de ung dung
  + Ton trong trai nghiem ca nhan cua tung khach hang
  + Phu hop cho nguoi moi bat dau tim hieu thuat so hoc
- Form lien he hien tai gom 4 truong:
  + Ho ten
  + Email
  + So dien thoai
  + Noi dung
- CTA form: Gui thong tin
- Thong bao sau submit: Thong tin cua ban da duoc ghi nhan. Linh Hoa Tam se lien he lai som.

TRANG 2: DANH SACH TIN TUC (/tin-tuc)
Muc tieu:
Tong hop toan bo bai viet dang co de nguoi dung chon doc theo chu de.

Cau truc:
- Hero page voi tieu de: Kien thuc thuat so hoc duoc trinh bay hien dai, am ap va de ung dung.
- Mo ta: bao gom kien thuc nen tang, goc nhin chua lanh trong cong viec va quan he.
- Danh sach bai viet dang hien thi theo card.
- Moi card gom:
  + Thumbnail label
  + Category
  + Date
  + Title
  + Description
  + CTA: Xem chi tiet

TRANG 3: CHI TIET BAI VIET (/tin-tuc/[slug])
Muc tieu:
Trinh bay noi dung chi tiet cho tung bai viet va giu nguoi dung trong he thong noi dung cua website.

Cau truc:
- Breadcrumb: Trang chu / Tin tuc / Ten bai viet
- Khoi thong tin dau bai:
  + Category
  + Title
  + Description
  + Date
- Khoi visual/noi dung mo dau voi thumbnail label va thong diep thuong hieu.
- Than bai viet duoc render theo nhieu section:
  + Moi section co heading
  + Moi heading co danh sach doan van noi dung

